notes.about: Demo data file for Takis Album Digital - Simulates all API responses
notes.customerId: Use 'DEMO_USER_001' as the customer ID for all API calls
notes.avatars: Avatars are SVG data URIs with Takis brand colors
notes.cardResources: Card resources point to placeholder URLs - should be replaced with actual asset paths
notes.packTypes: Pack type 1 = Normal (6 cards), Pack type 2 = Golden (8 cards with more special cards)
notes.inAlbum: Cards with inAlbum=true are placed in the album, false means duplicates
notes.identifiers: identifier field matches the card position in the album (card.identifier from cardsDatabase)
notes.duplicates: Cards 45 and 78 appear twice as duplicates (inAlbum=false)
notes.stickersToView: Pending gifts from friends that need to be accepted
notes.currentExchanges: Active exchange offers from other users
notes.metallic: Cards with metal=1 in cardsDatabase (special shiny cards)
notes.animated: Cards with anim=1 in cardsDatabase (video cards with .mp4)
notes.3dCards: Cards with has3d property have .glb 3D models available
